Hi Matthew,

Afraid I have another bug for you...

On 27/02/2024 17:42, Matthew Wilcox (Oracle) wrote:
<span class=3D"q">&gt; Hugetlb folios still get special treatment, but norm=
al large folios
&gt; can now be freed by free_unref_folios().  This should have a reasonabl=
e
&gt; performance impact, TBD.
&gt;=20
&gt; Signed-off-by: Matthew Wilcox (Oracle) &lt;willy@infradead.org&gt;
&gt; Reviewed-by: Ryan Roberts &lt;ryan.roberts@arm.com&gt;
</span>
When running some swap tests with this change (which is in mm-stable) prese=
