&gt;&gt; On 3/7/2024 4:56 PM,  wrote:
&gt;&gt;&gt; I just want to make sure I've understood correctly: CPU1's fol=
io_put()
&gt;&gt;&gt; is not the last reference, and it keeps iterating through the =
local
&gt;&gt;&gt; list. Then CPU2 does the final folio_put() which causes list_d=
el_init()
&gt;&gt;&gt; to modify the local list concurrently with CPU1's iteration, s=
o CPU1
&gt;&gt;&gt; probably goes into the weeds?
&gt;&gt;
