&gt;&gt; [   76.271344] head: order:0 entire_mapcount:1 nr_pages_mapped:0 p=
incount:0
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; This large folio has order 0? Maybe folio-&gt;_flags_1 was screwed=
?
&gt;&gt;
