Ah.  I'm not sure what 44b0dc848590 is -- probably a local commit, but
I guess you don't have fae7d834c43c in it which would prevent the nested
oops.  Nevertheless, the nested oops does tell us something interesting.

<span class=3D"q">&gt; So the very first line is from the first oops and th=
e rest is from the second. I guess we are racing with the page being freed?=
 I find the change in mapcount interesting; 0 -&gt; -128. Not sure why this=
